com.epam.jwd.task01.logic

Class JewelsInfoPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epam.jwd.task01.logic.JewelsInfoPrinter

  • public final class JewelsInfoPrinter
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class, containing only:

    a) methods for console output of GemstoneListCreator GemstoneList and NecklaceCreator Necklace, which both are instances of ArrayList collection and able to use all relevant methods;

    b) methods for console output of NecklaceCalculator methods for current Necklace instance.

    No instances of this class can exist, and all its fields and methods are static.

    See Also:
    GemstoneListCreator, NecklaceCreator, NecklaceCalculator
